| F002 | 未解决 | 计划虽然声明“单事务”，但修订后的具体实现仍在 `_sync_graph()` 内提前 `commit`，之后才继续 DA catalog / KP map，同步仍可能落入半同步状态（HIGH / `code-bug` / `defect_fix`），[plan.md#L168](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L168) [plan.md#L185](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L185) [plan.md#L208](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L208)。 |
| F003 | 未解决 | 前半段写的是“路径从 `settings` 读取”，但修订版正文又回到 `DEFAULT_KNOWLEDGE_DB`，且文中没有定义该常量，和“settings 收敛”自相矛盾（MED / `code-bug` / `defect_fix`），[plan.md#L103](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L103) [plan.md#L106](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L106) [plan.md#L195](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L195)。 |
| F004 | 未解决 | `pg_node` 兜底只覆盖了“文件不存在”分支；一旦文件存在，`result` 又被重置成仅含 `id` 的新对象，`PG 兜底`承诺并未真正保住（MED / `code-bug` / `defect_fix`），[plan.md#L460](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L460) [plan.md#L463](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L463) [plan.md#L469](/C:/Users/Administrator/docs/plans/2026-04-08-bio-demo-plan.md#L469)。 |
